headline: Las Vegas Sands Continues Underwriting for National Hispanic Institute's Las Vegas Program in a New Three-Year Engagement
summary: Las Vegas Sands (NYSE: LVS) will contribute nearly $350,000 for the 2024-2025 through 2026-2027 academic years to the National Hispanic Institute (NHI), continuing its Sands Cares support of the transformational leadership development program for Latino high school students in Las Vegas.
